description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of New York, which featured the return of Heather Holla Thomson, a vow of silence, and some baton twirling from Lu (unclear). After the recap, Danny sits down with Heather Morris, one of the stars of Glee and one of the producers of The Bystanders scripted podcast, which you can listen to NOW wherever you get your podcasts! They discuss the new show, favorite Glee moments, touring with Queen Beyonce, working with Queen Britney, her statement on Lea Michele, and more!


Heather Morris Interview: 24:14ish


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
